  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Graphic Designer",
  "description": "<p>If creativity is in you and graphic design is your passion, drop us a line. We are seeking talented and creative individuals to join our growing team.</p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Conceptualise and create visual artworks using Illustrator, Indesign and Photoshop</li><li>Develop concepts and visuals for clients with a creative and innovative flair</li><li>Work as a team or independently when needed in completing projects</li><li>To assist in art directing of photoshoots</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>Candidate must possess at least Diploma/Advanced/Higher/Graduate Diploma in Advertising/Media, Art/Design/Creative Multimedia or equivalent.</li><li>Candidates should preferably have at least 1 Year(s) of working experience in the related field. However, candidates with no prior experience will also be considered.</li><li>Mac and Adobe competent</li><li>Should have a good portfolio of visual artworks</li><li>Possess a positive, passionate and creative mind</li><li>Ability to perform under pressure with a strong desire to succeed</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>To apply for this position, please send in the following details:</p><p>1) Resume</p><p>2) Portfolio</p><p>3) Expected Salary</p><p>4) Availability</p><p><br /></p><p>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be invited for an interview.</p>",
